## Product Direction

This architecture changes the app from:

```txt
Voltaic tracker
```

into:

```txt
Universal aim-training progress app
```

Voltaic can still be the first and most polished benchmark.

Viscose can be added as the next benchmark pack.

Future benchmarks can be added without rebuilding the whole app.

The Aim Brain Engine becomes the real product core.

Benchmark packs become plug-ins that teach the engine how to understand each benchmark.

---

## Simplicity Rule

This benchmark pack system must stay easy to extend.

Adding a new benchmark should mostly mean adding a `pack.json`, optional adapter, and tests.

For the practical workflow, read:

